.Dd April 26, 2018
.Dt SHA1SUM 1
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm sha1sum
.Nd compute or check SHA1 message digest
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm
.Op Fl c
.Op Ar
.Sh DESCRIPTION
.Nm
writes SHA1
.Pq 160-bit
checksums of each
.Ar file
to the standard output. If
.Ar file
is a single dash
.Pq Sq -
or absent,
.Nm
reads from the standard input.
.Sh OPTIONS
.Bl -tag -width Ds
.It Fl c
Read list of SHA1 checksums from the given list and check them.
.El
.Sh EXIT STATUS
.Ex -std
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr cksum 1

